7️⃣ System Modules
7.1 Bus Tracking Module

Collect real-time latitude and longitude

Send location data every 5–10 seconds

Display live movement on interactive map

7.2 Passenger Counting Module
Option A – IR Sensor Based Counting

Two sensors at entry/exit

Increment/Decrement passenger count

Option B – AI-Based Detection (Advanced)

Camera at bus door

YOLO model detects people

Accurate real-time passenger count

7.3 Overcrowding Detection Module

Compare current passenger count with bus capacity

Trigger alerts when capacity exceeded

Display red alert indicators

7.4 Admin Dashboard

Live bus tracking map

Passenger count monitoring

Overcrowding alerts

Historical data reports

Peak hour analytics

Route performance analysis

7.5 Student Application

Students can:

View live bus location

Check seat availability

Receive overcrowding alerts

View estimated arrival time (ETA)

7.6 AI-Based Arrival Prediction

Analyze historical travel data

Predict delay patterns

Provide accurate ETA

